-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() Ammo = math.floor(input.getNumber(6)) GunPosX = input.getNumber(7) GunPosY = -input.getNumber(8) HDG = math.floor(input.getNumber(9)) GHDG = math.floor(input.getNumber(10)) MissilesLeft = math.floor(input.getNumber(11)) RocketsLeft = math.floor(input.getNumber(12)) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) isPressingZoomIn = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-10, 2, w-4, 8) isPressingZoomOut = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-10, 10, w-4, 16) if isPressingZoomIn then output.setBool(1, true) end if isPressingZoomOut then output.setBool(2, true) end if isPressed == false then output.setBool(2, false) output.setBool(1, false) end end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 150, 0)
screen.drawLine(0, h/2, (w/2)-10, h/2) screen.drawLine(w, h/2, (w/2)+10, h/2) screen.drawLine(w/2, h, w/2, (h/2)+ 10) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2, (w/2) +1, (h/2) + 1)
screen.drawText(w - 35, h - 21, "M:"..MissilesLeft) screen.drawText(w - 35, h - 14, "R:"..RocketsLeft) screen.drawText(w - 35, h - 7, "A:"..Ammo)
screen.drawText(1, h - 14, "H:"..HDG) screen.drawText(1, h - 7, "GH:"..GHDG)
screen.drawLine((w/2) + GunPosX* (w/2), 0, (w/2) + GunPosX * (w/2), 5) screen.drawLine(0, GunPosY * h , 5, GunPosY * h) screen.drawLine((w/2) - 1, 0, (w/2) - 1, 2) screen.drawLine((w/2) + 1, 0, (w/2) + 1, 2)
screen.drawRect(w - 10, 2, 6, 6) screen.drawRect(w - 10, 10, 6, 6) screen.drawLine(w - 8, 5, w - 5, 5) screen.drawLine(w - 7, 4, w - 7, 7) screen.drawLine(w - 8, 13, w - 5, 13)
end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

object.script:
zoo = 5 zoom = 0--1.431 x = 0--200 y = 0--100 function onTick() inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) b = input.getNumber(5) worldX = input.getNumber(6) worldY = input.getNumber(7) NM = input.getBool(2) isPressingZoomIn = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w - 8,2,6,6) isPressingZoomOut = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w - 8,8,6,6) if isPressingZoomIn then zoom = zoom - 0.01 elseif isPressingZoomOut then zoom = zoom + 0.01 end isPressingXPlus = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-8, h-14, 6,6) isPressingXMinus = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-22, h-14, 6,6) isPressingYPlus = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-15, h-21, 6,6) isPressingYMinus = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-15, h-7, 6,6) isPressingReset = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-15, h-14, 6,6) if isPressingReset then x= 0--200 y= 0--100 end if isPressingXPlus then x = x + 0.75 * (zoo^(zoom + 1.431)) elseif isPressingXMinus then x = x - 0.75 * (zoo^(zoom + 1.431)) end if isPressingYPlus then y = y + 0.75 * (zoo^(zoom + 1.431)) elseif isPressingYMinus then y = y - 0.75 * (zoo^(zoom + 1.431)) end if zoom < -1.431 then zoom = -1.431 end if zoom > 2.431 then zoom = 2.431 end output.setNumber(1, zoo^zoom) output.setNumber(2, x + worldX) output.setNumber(3, y + worldY) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() if NM == true then screen.setMapColorOcean(1, 1, 1, 255) screen.setMapColorShallows(10, 10, 10, 200) screen.setMapColorLand(50, 50, 50, 100) screen.setMapColorGrass(150, 150, 150, 50) screen.setMapColorSand(20, 20, 20, 255) screen.setMapColorSnow(255, 255, 255, 100) else screen.setMapColorOcean(0, 20, 28, 255) screen.setMapColorShallows(0, 38, 59, 200) screen.setMapColorLand(60, 60, 60, 250) screen.setMapColorGrass(00, 56, 7, 100) screen.setMapColorSand(80, 80, 0, 105) screen.setMapColorSnow(255, 255, 255, 100) end screen.drawMap(x + worldX, y + worldY, zoo^zoom) pixelX, pixelY = map.mapToScreen(x + worldX, y + worldY, zoo^ zoom, w, h, worldX, worldY)
screen.setColor(20*b, 2*b, 2*b) -- Map Player Location screen.drawRect(pixelX, pixelY, 2,2) screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 50) screen.drawRect(pixelX - 1, pixelY - 1, 4,4) screen.setColor(255*b, 255*b, 255*b, 100) screen.drawCircleF(pixelX + 1, pixelY + 1, 1)
if isPressingZoomIn then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w - 7,3,5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,2100*b, 200) end if isPressingZoomOut then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w - 7,9,5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end screen.drawLine(w-6,5,w-3,5) screen.drawLine(w-5,4,w-5,7) screen.drawLine(w-6,11,w-3,11) screen.drawLine(w-5,17,w-5,39) screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b,2*b, 150) -- Zoom Slider screen.drawRectF(w-7, (zoo^zoom * 0.38) + 20, 5, 3) if isPressingXPlus then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w-7, h-13, 5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end if isPressingXMinus then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w-21, h-13, 5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end if isPressingYPlus then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w-14, h-20, 5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end if isPressingYMinus then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w-14, h-6, 5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end if isPressingReset then screen.setColor(50*b, 2*b, 2*b, 150) screen.drawRectF(w-14, h-13, 5,5) screen.setColor(100*b,100*b,100*b, 200) end --screen.setColor(20,20,20) --screen.drawLine(w-24,h,w-24,h-22) end

AP = false AH = false NM = false clicked = false function onTick() inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) waypointReached = input.getBool(7) speed = math.floor(input.getNumber(5)) bearing = math.floor(input.getNumber(6)) altitude = math.floor(input.getNumber(7)) fuel = math.floor(input.getNumber(8)) fuelCap = math.floor(input.getNumber(9)) fuelPerc = math.floor((fuel/fuelCap) * 100) isPressingAP = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 20, h-10, 17, h) isPressingAH = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 37, h-10, 16, h) isPressingNM = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 53, h-10, 17, h) if isPressingAP and AP == false and clicked == false then clicked = true AP = true AH = true elseif isPressingAP and AP == true and clicked == false then clicked = true AP = false end if waypointReached == true and AP == true then AP = false end if isPressingAH and AH == false and clicked == false then clicked = true AH = true elseif isPressingAH and AH == true and clicked == false then clicked = true AH = false end if isPressingNM and NM == false and clicked == false then clicked = true NM = true elseif isPressingNM and NM == true and clicked == false then clicked = true NM = false end if isPressed == false then clicked = false end output.setBool(1, AP) output.setBool(2, AH) output.setBool(3, NM) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(2, 2, 2, 100) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 20, h)
screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawCircleF(w - 13 , h -11, 12) screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawCircle(w - 13, h -11, 12) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(20, h-10, w-20, h) screen.drawRectF(w-12, h-24, 12, 24)
screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawLine(20, h, 20, h-10) screen.drawLine(w-12, h-24, w, h-24)
screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(0, 1, 20, 6, "SPD", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 7, 20, 6, speed, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 15, 20, 6, "ALT", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 21, 20, 6, altitude, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 29, 20, 6, "BRNG", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 35, 20, 6, bearing, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 43, 20, 6, "FUEL", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(0, 49, 20, 6, fuelPerc, 0, 0)
screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRect(2, 55, 16, 3) screen.setColor(100, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(3, 56, ((fuel/fuelCap) * 15), 2)
screen.setColor(100,100,100, 200) -- Movement Arrows screen.drawRect(w-15, h-20, 6,6) --YPlus screen.drawLine(w-13, h-17, w-12, h-18) screen.drawLine(w-11, h-17, w-12, h-19)
screen.drawRect(w-15, h-8, 6,6) --YMinus screen.drawLine(w-13, h-5, w-12, h-5) screen.drawLine(w-11, h-5, w-12, h-3)
screen.drawRect(w-21, h-14, 6,6) --XMinus screen.drawLine(w-18, h-10, w-19, h-12) screen.drawLine(w-18, h-12, w-19, h-13)
screen.drawRect(w-9, h-14, 6,6) -- XPlus screen.drawLine(w-6, h-10, w-4, h-12) screen.drawLine(w-6, h-12, w-5, h-13)
screen.drawRect(w-15, h-14, 6,6) -- Reset screen.drawRect(w-13, h-12, 2, 2)
screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) --screen.drawText(w/2+2, h-19, "Lat:") --screen.drawText(w/2+2, h-13, "Long:") end

function onTick() hour = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)) minutes1 = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)) if minutes1 >=0 and minutes1 < 10 then minutes = "0" .. minutes1 else minutes = minutes1 end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawText(61, 1, hour .. ":" .. minutes) end

-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() AP = input.getBool(1) AH = input.getBool(2) NM = input.getBool(3)
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawRect(20, h-10, 17, h) -- Buttons - AP screen.drawRect(37, h-10, 16, h) -- AH screen.drawRect(53, h-10, 17, h) -- NM
screen.setColor(50, 50, 50)
screen.drawTextBox(38, h-9, 16, 10, "AH", 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(53, h-9, 17, 10, "NM", 0, 0)
if AP == true then screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawRectF(21, h-9, 16, h-1) screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawTextBox(20, h-9, 17, 10, "AP", 0, 0) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawText(22, 1, "AP")
else screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(21, h-9, 16, h-1) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawTextBox(20, h-9, 17, 10, "AP", 0, 0) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30, 100) screen.drawText(22, 1, "AP") end if AH == true then screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawRectF(38, h-9, 15, h-1) screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawTextBox(38, h-9, 16, 10, "AH", 0, 0) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawText(35, 1, "AH") else screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(38, h-9, 15, h-1) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawTextBox(38, h-9, 16, 10, "AH", 0, 0) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30, 100) screen.drawText(35, 1, "AH") end if NM == true then screen.setColor(40, 40, 40) screen.drawRectF(54, h-9, 16, h-1) screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawTextBox(53, h-9, 17, 10, "NM", 0, 0) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawText(48, 1, "NM") else screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(54, h-9, 16, h-1) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawTextBox(53, h-9, 17, 10, "NM", 0, 0) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30, 100) screen.drawText(48, 1, "NM") end
end

screen.setColor(2, 2, 2, 100) --Transparent Backgrounds screen.drawRectF(w-9,7,9,h-27) screen.drawRectF(20,0,w,7) screen.setColor(100,100,100, 200) --Top Text screen.drawRect(w - 8,2,6,6) -- Zoom Buttons screen.drawRect(w - 8,8,6,6) end

waypointX = input.getNumber(6) waypointY = input.getNumber(7)

object.script:
pi=math.pi function onTick() alt=input.getNumber(1) spd=input.getNumber(2)*3.6 dSpd=input.getNumber(6)*3.6 dAlt=input.getNumber(7)*60 tF=input.getNumber(3)*2*pi tL=input.getNumber(4)*2*pi tV=input.getNumber(5)*2*pi bearing=-input.getNumber(8)%1*360 hSpd=input.getNumber(9)*1.943844 vSpd=input.getNumber(10)*1.943844 dHSpd=input.getNumber(11)*1.943844*60 dVSpd=input.getNumber(12)*1.943844*60 background=input.getBool(1) sway=property.getNumber("Sway Amount") end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() sX= sway*w*-dHSpd/1000 sY= sway*h*-dVSpd/1000
sX = spd > 20 and sX or 0 sY = spd > 20 and sY or 0 r1=0.17*w r2=0.5*r1 roll=-math.atan(tL,tV) r=(w+h)*2 if background then x1=w/2-r*math.cos(roll)-math.sin(roll)*tF*h/1+sX y1=h/2-r*math.sin(roll)+math.cos(roll)*tF*h/1+sY x2=w/2+r*math.cos(roll)-math.sin(roll)*tF*h/1+sX y2=h/2+r*math.sin(roll)+math.cos(roll)*tF*h/1+sY x3=w/2+r*math.cos(roll-pi/2)-math.sin(roll)*tF*h/1+sX y3=h/2+r*math.sin(roll-pi/2)+math.cos(roll)*tF*h/1+sY x4=w/2+r*math.cos(roll+pi/2)-math.sin(roll)*tF*h/1+sX y4=h/2+r*math.sin(roll+pi/2)+math.cos(roll)*tF*h/1+sY screen.setColor(70,45,25) screen.drawTriangleF(x1,y1,x2,y2,x4,y4) screen.setColor(30,85,113) screen.drawTriangleF(x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3) end screen.setColor(0,32,0) for a=-10,10 do p=tF+math.pi/18*a r=r2 if a%2==0 then r=r1 end x1=w/2-r*math.cos(roll)-math.sin(roll)*p*h/1+sX y1=h/2-r*math.sin(roll)+math.cos(roll)*p*h/1+sY x2=w/2+r*math.cos(roll)-math.sin(roll)*p*h/1+sX y2=h/2+r*math.sin(roll)+math.cos(roll)*p*h/1+sY screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) if a%2==0 then screen.drawText(x2,y2,-a*10) end end screen.drawLine(20+5+sX,h/2+sY,w/2-5+sX,h/2+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+5+sX,h/2+sY,w-20-5+sX,h/2+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2-5+sX,h/2+sY,w/2+sX,h/2+5+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+5+sX,h/2+sY,w/2+sX,h/2+5+sY) rad1=w/2-2-5 rad2=w/2-7-5 rad3=w/2-10-5 rad4=w/2-15-5 screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(pi/12)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(pi/12)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(pi/12)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(pi/12)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(-pi/12)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(-pi/12)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(-pi/12)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(-pi/12)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(pi/6)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(pi/6)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(pi/6)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(pi/6)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(-pi/6)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(-pi/6)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(-pi/6)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(-pi/6)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(pi/4)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(pi/4)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(pi/4)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(pi/4)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+rad1*math.sin(-pi/4)+sX,h/2+rad1*math.cos(-pi/4)+sY,w/2+rad2*math.sin(-pi/4)+sX,h/2+rad2*math.cos(-pi/4)+sY) screen.drawLine(w/2+sX,h/2+rad1+sY,w/2+sX,h/2+rad2+sY) screen.drawTriangleF(w/2+rad3*math.sin(-roll)+sX,h/2+rad3*math.cos(-roll)+sY,w/2+rad4*math.sin(-roll-pi/30)+sX,h/2+rad4*math.cos(-roll-pi/30)+sY,w/2+rad4*math.sin(-roll+pi/30)+sX,h/2+rad4*math.cos(-roll+pi/30)+sY) screen.drawText(5+sX,h/2-2+sY,string.format("%03d",math.floor(spd+0.5))) screen.drawText(w-15-5+sX,h/2-2+sY,string.format("%03d",math.floor(alt/100+0.5))) screen.drawText(w-20-5+sX,h/2+5+sY,string.format("%+04d",math.floor(dAlt+0.5))) screen.drawText(w/2-7+sX,2+5+sY,string.format("%03d",math.floor(bearing))) vX=w/2+w/2*math.atan(-hSpd/spd) vY=h/2+h/2*math.atan(-vSpd/spd) vX = spd > 10 and vX or w/2 vY = spd > 10 and vY or h/2 screen.drawRect(vX-2+sX,vY-2+sY,4,4) screen.drawLine(vX+2+sX,vY+sY,vX+6+sX,vY+sY) screen.drawLine(vX-2+sX,vY+sY,vX-6+sX,vY+sY) screen.drawLine(vX+sX,vY-2+sY,vX+sX,vY-6+sY) end

targets = {}
fov = 0.05
function onTick() for i = 0, 6 do targets[i] = {dist = input.getNumber(4*i+1),az =input.getNumber(4*i+2),elv = input.getNumber(4*i+3)} end spd = input.getNumber(30) dHSpd = input.getNumber(31)*3.6*60 dVSpd = input.getNumber(32)*3.6*60
enabled = input.getBool(32)
sway = property.getNumber("Sway Amount") end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0,32,0) if enabled then f = fov--math.atan((w/h)*math.tan(fov)) sX= sway*w*-dHSpd/1000 sY= sway*h*-dVSpd/1000 sX = spd > 20 and sX or 0 sY = spd > 20 and sY or 0
for i, v in pairs(targets) do if v.dist > 0 then x = w/2 + (w/2) * (math.tan(v.az)/math.tan(f)) y = h/2 - (h/2) * (math.tan(v.elv)/math.tan(fov)) screen.drawRect(x+sX-4,y+sY-4,8,8) end end end end

object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() Ammo = math.floor(input.getNumber(6)) GunPosX = input.getNumber(7) GunPosY = -input.getNumber(8) HDG = math.floor(input.getNumber(9)) GHDG = math.floor(input.getNumber(10)) MissilesLeft = math.floor(input.getNumber(11)) RocketsLeft = math.floor(input.getNumber(12)) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) isPressingZoomIn = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-10, 2, w-4, 8) isPressingZoomOut = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-10, 10, w-4, 16) if isPressingZoomIn then output.setBool(1, true) end if isPressingZoomOut then output.setBool(2, true) end if isPressed == false then output.setBool(2, false) output.setBool(1, false) end end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 150, 0)
screen.drawLine(0, h/2, (w/2)-10, h/2) screen.drawLine(w, h/2, (w/2)+10, h/2) screen.drawLine(w/2, h, w/2, (h/2)+ 10) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2, (w/2) +1, (h/2) + 1)
screen.drawText(w - 40, h - 21, "MSLS:" .. MissilesLeft) screen.drawText(w - 40, h - 14, "RKTS:" .. RocketsLeft) screen.drawText(w - 40, h - 7, "Ammo:" .. Ammo)
screen.drawText(1, h - 14, "HDG:" .. HDG) screen.drawText(1, h - 7, "GHDG:" .. GHDG)
screen.drawLine((w/2) + GunPosX* (w/2), 0, (w/2) + GunPosX * (w/2), 5) screen.drawLine(0, GunPosY * h , 5, GunPosY * h) screen.drawLine((w/2) - 1, 0, (w/2) - 1, 2) screen.drawLine((w/2) + 1, 0, (w/2) + 1, 2)
screen.drawRect(w - 10, 2, 6, 6) screen.drawRect(w - 10, 10, 6, 6) screen.drawLine(w - 8, 5, w - 5, 5) screen.drawLine(w - 7, 4, w - 7, 7) screen.drawLine(w - 8, 13, w - 5, 13)
end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

object.script:
gb=input.getBool gn=input.getNumber sb=output.setBool sn=output.setNumber
cache={} cacheCounter=1 maxCache=50 contacts={}
radar=0
pn=property.getNumber rangeShort=pn("Short Range") rangeMedium=pn("Medium Range") rangeLong=pn("Long Range") rangeMode=3 targetRange=rangeLong maxRange=rangeShort lastFrameClick=false
function onTick() --8 possible hits, gb 1-8 screenClick=gb(32) if screenClick then if not lastFrameClick then lastFrameClick=true rangeMode=rangeMode+1 if rangeMode>3 then rangeMode=1 end end else lastFrameClick=false end if rangeMode==1 then targetRange=rangeShort elseif rangeMode==2 then targetRange=rangeMedium else targetRange=rangeLong end
if targetRange~=maxRange then dt=rangeLong/100 if maxRange<targetRange then maxRange=math.min(maxRange+dt,targetRange) else maxRange=math.max(maxRange-dt,targetRange) end end
radar=gn(32)
--4 numbers in sequence: range, azimuth, elevation, elapsed time since detected. for i=1,maxCache do contact=cache[i] if contact then contact[5]=contact[5]*0.95 cache[i]=contact end end --For display purposes, we process it into 3 numbers in sequence: --flat range (negative for airborn), azimuth, and time. contacts={} for i=1,8 do contact=interpret(i) contacts[i]=contact sb(i,contact[1]) if contact[4] > 0.1 then sn(i*3,-contact[2]) else sn(i*3,contact[2]) end sn(i*3+1, contact[3]) sn(i*3+2, contact[5]) end end
function interpret(index) exists=gb(index) oindex=index*4-3 range=gn(oindex) azimuth=gn(oindex+1) elevation=gn(oindex+2) time=gn(oindex+3)--garbage contact={exists,range,azimuth,elevation,255} if exists then cache[cacheCounter]=contact cacheCounter=cacheCounter+1 if cacheCounter>maxCache then cacheCounter=1 end end return contact
-- nindex=index*3
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen s=screen function onDraw() w2=s.getWidth()/2 h2=s.getHeight()/2
s.setColor(0,255,0,100) s.drawCircle(w2,h2,h2) dx=math.sin(radar*math.pi*2)*h2 dy=-math.cos(radar*math.pi*2)*h2 s.drawLine(w2,h2,w2+dx,h2+dy)
step=25000 if maxRange<50000 then step=5000 elseif maxRange<1500 then step=250 elseif maxRange<3000 then step=1000 elseif maxRange<10000 then step=2500 elseif maxRange<3000 then step=500 end
s.setColor(0,255,0,100) for i=step,maxRange,step do percent=i/maxRange s.drawCircle(w2,h2,h2*percent) end
for i=1,maxCache do contact=cache[i] if contact then percent=contact[2]/maxRange dx=math.sin(contact[3]*math.pi*2)*h2*percent dy=-math.cos(contact[3]*math.pi*2)*h2*percent if contact[4]>.02 then s.setColor(255,255,0,contact[5]) else s.setColor(0,255,255,contact[5]) end s.drawRect(dx+w2,h2+dy,1,1) end end
--s.setColor(255,255,255,255) -- for i=1,8 do -- y=i*6+6 -- contact=contacts[i] -- if contact[1]==false then -- screen.drawText(2,y,"No contact") -- else -- screen.drawText(2,y,contact[3]) -- end -- end end

object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() scan= input.getBool(2) lock= input.getBool(3) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) mute= input.getBool(4) auto= input.getBool(5)
isPressingMute = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, w/2, w, h/4)
isPressingAuto = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, w/4*3, w, h/4)
-- Set the composite output, on/off channel 1 output.setBool(1, isPressingMute) output.setBool(2, isPressingAuto) end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(1, 1, 1) screen.drawLine(0, h / 4, w, h/4) screen.drawLine(0, h/2, w, h/2) screen.drawLine(0, h/4*3,w, h/4*3)
if lock==true then screen.setColor(100, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, w, h/4) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, 2, w, h/4, "lock") else screen.setColor(10, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, w, h/4) screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, 2, w, h/4, "lock") end
if scan==true then screen.setColor(0, 100, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/4+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, h/4+2, w, h/4, "scan") else screen.setColor(0, 10, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/4+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(10, 10, 10) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, h/4+2, w, h/4, "scan") end
if mute==true then screen.setColor(0, 50, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/2+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, h/2+2, w, h/4, "mute") else screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/2+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(0, 50, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, h/2+2, w, h/4, "mute") end
if auto==true then screen.setColor(0, 50, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/4*3+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawTextBox(2, h/4*3+2, w, h/4, "manual") else screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, h/4*3+1, w, h/4-1) screen.setColor(0, 50, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w/5, h/4*3+2, w, h/4, "auto") end
end
